description: [``botocore``] This is release adds support for Amazon VPC Reachability Analyzer to analyze path through a Transit Gateway.
[``botocore``] This Patch Manager release supports creating, updating, and deleting Patch Baselines for Rocky Linux OS.
[``botocore``] Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where shapes were marked as unboxed and were not serialized and sent over the wire, causing an API error from the service.
